componentDescription: A TableCell based component for placing inside TableFooter for pagination.

propDescriptions.ActionsComponent:
The component used for displaying the actions.
Either a string to use a HTML element or a component.
propDescriptions.backIconButtonProps: Props applied to the back arrow IconButton component.
propDescriptions.classes: Override or extend the styles applied to the component. See CSS API below for more details.
propDescriptions.component:
The component used for the root node.
Either a string to use a HTML element or a component.
propDescriptions.count:
The total number of rows.

To enable server side pagination for an unknown number of items, provide -1.
propDescriptions.labelRowsPerPage: Customize the rows per page label. For localization purposes, you can use the provided translations.
propDescriptions.nextIconButtonProps: Props applied to the next arrow IconButton element.
propDescriptions.onRowsPerPageChange:
Callback fired when the number of rows per page is changed.

@param {object} event The event source of the callback.
propDescriptions.page: The zero-based index of the current page.
propDescriptions.rowsPerPage:
The number of rows per page.

Set -1 to display all the rows.
propDescriptions.rowsPerPageOptions:
Customizes the options of the rows per page select field. If less than two options are
available, no select field will be displayed.
propDescriptions.SelectProps: Props applied to the rows per page Select element.

root.description: Styles applied to the root element.

toolbar.description: Styles applied to the Toolbar component.

spacer.description: Styles applied to the spacer element.

caption.description: Styles applied to the caption Typography components if {{conditions}}.

selectRoot.description: Styles applied to the Select component root element.

select.description: Styles applied to the Select component `select` class.

selectIcon.description: Styles applied to the Select component `icon` class.

menuItem.description: Styles applied to the MenuItem component.

actions.description: Styles applied to the internal `TablePaginationActions` component.
